{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/LEET/L2530MaximalScoreAfterApplyingKOperations/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"2530. Maximal Score After Applying K Operations","date":"October 14, 2024"},"html":"<h1>문제 설명</h1>\n<p>이 문제는 하나의 배열이 주어졌을 때, 배열의 최댓값을 찾아서 score에 더해주는 과정을 k번 반복하였을 때, 최종 score를 구하는 문제이다.<br>\n이때, 더해진 값은 3으로 나누어 올림한 값으로 대체한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2530\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/95646865d5deafd6c697d229bb37fae2/5a190/2530.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95646865d5deafd6c697d229bb37fae2/772e8/2530.png 200w,\n/static/95646865d5deafd6c697d229bb37fae2/e17e5/2530.png 400w,\n/static/95646865d5deafd6c697d229bb37fae2/5a190/2530.png 800w,\n/static/95646865d5deafd6c697d229bb37fae2/3fca6/2530.png 1112w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>풀이 및 해설</h2>\n<h2>1차 풀이</h2>\n<p>k만큼 반복하면서, 최대값을 찾아서 더해주는 방식으로 풀이하였다.</p>\n<p>그러나, 이렇게 할 경우 Time Limit Exceeded가 발생하였다.</p>\n<h2>풀이</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">class Solution:\n    def maxKelements(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -> int:\n        score = 0\n        for i in range(k):\n            max_value = max(nums)\n            max_index = nums.index(max_value)\n            score += max_value\n            nums[max_index] = math.ceil(nums[max_index]/3)\n        return score\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Complexity Analysis</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>O(n*k) : n은 nums의 길이, k는 반복 횟수</li>\n</ul>\n<p>너무 느리다.</p>\n<h2>2차 풀이</h2>\n<p>따라서, 최대값을 찾는 과정을 heap을 이용하여 최적화하였다.</p>\n<h2>풀이</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">import heapq\nimport math\n\nclass Solution:\n    def maxKelements(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -> int:\n        score = 0\n        heap = [-num for num in nums]\n        heapq.heapify(heap)\n\n        for _ in range(k):\n            max_value = -heapq.heappop(heap)\n            score += max_value\n            heapq.heappush(heap, -math.ceil(max_value /3))\n        \n        return score\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>list를 heap으로 변환할 때, 음수로 변환하여 최대값을 찾을 수 있도록 하였다.</li>\n<li>최대값을 찾은 후, 다시 heap에 넣을 때는 3으로 나눈 값을 올림하여 넣어주었다.</li>\n<li>이를 k번 반복하면서 score를 계산하였다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Complexity Analysis</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"tc\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e690ec4ff6f7c5d62391b091257faf5e/5a190/tc.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e690ec4ff6f7c5d62391b091257faf5e/772e8/tc.png 200w,\n/static/e690ec4ff6f7c5d62391b091257faf5e/e17e5/tc.png 400w,\n/static/e690ec4ff6f7c5d62391b091257faf5e/5a190/tc.png 800w,\n/static/e690ec4ff6f7c5d62391b091257faf5e/3fca6/tc.png 1112w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>시간 복잡도</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>최대값을 찾는 과정이 O(logn)이므로, 전체 시간 복잡도는 O(klogn)이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>공간 복잡도</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>heap을 사용하였으므로, O(n)이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Constraint Analysis</h2>\n<pre><code>Constraints:\n1 &#x3C;= nums.length, k &#x3C;= 10^5\n1 &#x3C;= nums[i] &#x3C;= 10^9\n</code></pre>\n<h1>References</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/maximal-score-after-applying-operations/\">2530. Maximal Score After Applying K Operations</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/LEET/L2530MaximalScoreAfterApplyingKOperations/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}